---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Workplaces from '../components/Workplaces.astro';
import TechnologyTag from '../components/TechnologyTag.astro';
---

<style>
  body {
    background-image: url('../assets/background-optimised.png');

    @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
      background-image: url('../assets/background.png');
    }
  }
  main {
    @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
      max-width: 768px;
    }
  }

  section {
    @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
      margin-block-end: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block-start: 0;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      display: block;
      max-width: 1200px;
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }

    .title-smaller {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.75em;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    margin-block-end: 1.25rem;
  }

  .technologies {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style-type: none;

    li {
      margin-inline-end: 0.5rem;
      margin-block-end: 0.25rem;
      display: inline-block;
      line-height: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Senior Front End Software Engineer - Matteo Pieroni">
  <main>
    <h1>
      Hello there!<br /><span class="title-smaller"
        >I'm Matteo Pieroni, Front End Software Engineer</span
      >
    </h1>

    <section>
      <p>
        Throughout my time as a software engineer, I was lucky enough to work
        with amazing people and on a variety of different products, some used by
        millions of people.
      </p>
      <p>
        Since the old days of Wordpress and jQuery, I've picked up a couple
        specific focuses that I really enjoy: accessibility and architecture. I
        love building well thought out, performant, and maintainable software
        that is usable by as many folks as possible.
      </p>
      <p>
        In my spare time, I am a certified safari guide and an enthusiastic
        wildlife photographer. I love exploring nature and capturing moments
        through my camera lens, with the importance of detail, patience, and
        perspective at the forefront of my thoughts â€” qualities I bring to my
        engineering work as well.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Technologies</h2>
      <ul class="technologies">
        <li><TechnologyTag>HTML</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>CSS</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>Js</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>React</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>NextJs</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>testing-library</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>Jest</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>GraphQL</TechnologyTag></li>
        <li><TechnologyTag>Vercel</TechnologyTag></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <Workplaces />
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
